for what he really believed in.

00:28:23.640 --> 00:28:25.620
Because when he was
confronted with the idea

00:28:25.620 --> 00:28:31.150
that I've got to protect these
people, not just feed them,

00:28:31.150 --> 00:28:32.170
so what does that mean?

00:28:32.170 --> 00:28:35.290
Well, it means I need to become
