00:28:35.290 --> 00:28:37.100
that I can actually do that.

00:28:37.100 --> 00:28:39.270
That's really holding
yourself accountable.

00:28:39.270 --> 00:28:41.580
But he's also very
good at taking

00:28:41.580 --> 00:28:44.670
what he had cultivated
in one part of his life,

00:28:44.670 --> 00:28:46.950
how he learned about
human resilience

00:28:46.950 --> 00:28:49.950
in these terrible circumstances
and how people survive

00:28:49.950 --> 00:28:53.000
by serving others,
and applying that

00:28:53.000 --> 00:28:55.410
in the founding of
The Mission Continues.

00:28:55.410 --> 00:28:58.510
That's the founding idea.

00:28:58.510 --> 00:29:01.120
Wounded veterans want
to continue to serve.

00:29:01.120 --> 00:29:03.780
Let's create opportunities
for them to do that.

00:29:03.780 --> 00:29:06.180
And that's what The
Mission Continues is,

00:29:06.180 --> 00:29:08.240
and indeed the first
fellow-- and now

00:29:08.240 --> 00:29:11.580
there have been hundreds and
