global market

00:31:27.270 --> 00:31:29.140
share than he's ever
had in his life.

00:31:29.140 --> 00:31:30.580
They just continue to grow.

00:31:30.580 --> 00:31:31.960
Why is that?

00:31:31.960 --> 00:31:35.250
Because he's constantly
pushing the boundaries

00:31:35.250 --> 00:31:36.800
of his creative talent.

00:31:36.800 --> 00:31:39.000
And he makes other people
around him do the same.

00:31:39.000 --> 00:31:40.930
He creates cultures
of innovation.

00:31:40.930 --> 00:31:43.750
All right, so this is
a very quick snapshot

00:31:43.750 --> 00:31:46.500
of what these skills are--
what it means to be real,

00:31:46.500 --> 00:31:50.590
to know what matters, to be
those values wherever you are,

00:31:50.590 --> 00:31:54.870
to strive to align what you
do with what you care about

00:31:54.870 --> 00:31:58.790
and to convey what matters
to you through stories;

00:31:58.790 --> 00:32:00.520
to be able to
envision your future

00:32:00.520 --> 00:32:05.060
and hold yourself accountable
for pursuing what matters most;

00:32:05.060 --> 00:32:10.380
to be whole, clarifying
what matters most to you;

00:32:10.380 --> 00:32:13.160
to be helping other people
all the time so that you're

00:32:13.160 --> 00:32:16.430
building supportive networks
and taking what you have in one

00:32:16.430 --> 00:32:18.610
part of your life and
applying it in the others;

00:32:18.610 --> 00:32:22.134
and being smart about how
you manage boundaries.

00:32:22.134 --> 00:32:24.050
Sometimes that means
creating firm boundaries,

00:32:24.050 --> 00:32:26.650
where you focus just on one
person or one thing at a time.

00:32:26.650 --> 00:32:29.330
Other times it
means merging them.

00:32:29.330 --> 00:32:31.970
But it's all about
conscious, deliberate choice

00:32:31.970 --> 00:32:35.610
and experimentation and weaving
the different pieces together

00:32:35.610 --> 00:32:37.420
in a way that works
for you and for them.

00:32:37.420 --> 00:32:40.010
To be innovative means
focusing our results

00:32:40.010 --> 00:32:42.930
and letting the means
for their achievement

00:32:42.930 --> 00:32:45.790
happen flexibly among
the people around you.

00:32:45.790 --> 00:32:48.520
To be creative about
resolving conflicts--

00:32:48.520 --> 00:32:52.290
where you see a conflict, look
differently at the situation.

00:32:52.290 --> 00:32:56.230
Where is there an opportunity
for this to be a win-win?

00:32:56.230 --> 00:32:58.774
And to be looking
back and saying,

00:32:58.774 --> 00:33:00.940
we don't have to do it that
way, and looking forward

00:33:00.940 --> 00:33:03.580
and saying, how can we
do it some way different,

00:33:03.580 --> 00:33:05.790
and having the
courage and support

00:33:05.790 --> 00:33:08.390
to try new ways of
getting things done.

00:33:08.390 --> 00:33:10.930
And finally to be teaching
other people all the time.

00:33:10.930 --> 00:33:11.930
So these are the skills.

